    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatione Domini millesimo trigesimo tertio,
                        die undecima mensis augusti, indictione prima, situm in claustro <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1480">Sancti
                            Stefani Maioris</orgName>. Peto a te in Dei nomine domno <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1574">Guidone</persName> gratia Dei <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Linen #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Operae #Canals #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, ad confirmandum a
                        domno <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Aurelius">Aurelio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs> ipsius monasterii, uti mihi in Christi nomine
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus Punga">Petro Punga</name></persName>
                        petitori pro me et pro <persName><name ref="Anna">Anna</name></persName>
                        iugale mea seu filiis nostris masculis – et qualis de nobis obierit sine
                        filio vel filia eorum parti acedat illi qui ut supra supravixerit – si iuste
                        et rationabiliter a vobis petivimus et ab aliis minime detineri videtur per
                            <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellum</rs> concedatis nobis
                        rem iuris prefati monasterii vestri, idest <rs key="#Mansi">medietatem
                            integram de uno manso</rs> cum <rs key="Landed_possessions">terris</rs>,
                            <rs key="Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs
                            key="Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>, <rs>arbustis</rs>, <rs
                            key="Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs> atque cum omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, quam nos habemus et detinemus per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">anteriorem libellum</rs> iuris
                        vestri monasterii, constitutam in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Linen #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Operae #Canals #Levies"
                            ref="#places/4643"><geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Linen #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Operae #Canals #Levies" ref="#estates/2491"
                            >Sezata</geogName></placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Linen #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Operae #Canals #Levies"
                            ref="#places/4606">Campo Domnico</placeName>, <rs key="#Plebs"
                            >plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1490">Sancti Iohannis in
                                <placeName ref="#places/3527">Axiata</placeName></orgName>;
                        habendum, tenendum, supersedendum, cultandum, laborandum et in omnibus
                        meliorandum in annis advenientibus viginti et novem ad renovandum; sub <rs
                            key="#Levies">terratico</rs> de omni <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">labore
                            maiore</rs> modium quintum, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> manna quinta, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">minuto</rs> sextum, <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs>
                        anforam terciam, arbore semel ponendo; et dare vobis debeamus omni secundo
                        anno in Natale <rs key="#Animals">unam spallam</rs> et omni secundo anno in
                        Pascha <rs key="#Sheep">agnum</rs> unum et omni anno in sancto Apolenare
                        focaciam unam et <rs key="#Poultry">pullum</rs> unum; et omni anno pro <rs
                            key="#Levies">glandatico</rs> et <rs key="#Levies">lignario</rs> solidos
                        tres denariorum Veneticorum; pro <rs key="#Exenia">exenio</rs> de grano
                        ariale starium unum et medium et unam galinam omni secundo anno; et tollere
                        debeamus de ipsa terra tornaturiam unam et mediam pro arato et area et <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs> et <rs key="#Canals">canalibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Operae">opera</rs> et servicia secundum usus ipsius loci;
                        pervectum totum terraticum domnicum et aliam dacionem per nos petitores
                        usque in hac civitate <placeName ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>, in
                        canniva vestra Sancti Stefani Maioris; et non liceat nobis triturare neque
                        vindemiare sine vestra iussione vat(a) vestrum <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missum</rs> cum honore et
                        hobbedientia susipere debeamus; et non liceat nobis petitoribus neque
                        nostris filiis ipsam rem totam nec partem vendere neque aliquo modo alienare
                        nisi inter nos aut inter monasterium vestrum neque ad placitum vel
                        districtum alicuius ire nisi vobis. Pro eo quia exinde damus vobis
                        calciariis nomine solidos undecim denariorum Luccentium inforciatorum. Si
                        quis vero partis nostre contra hanc petitionem ire temptaverit, det pars
                        parti fidem servanti nomine pene <rs key="#Penalty">auri unciam unam</rs> et
                        soluta pena maneat firma hec peticio. Ego Petrus Dei misericordia Ravennas
                        tabellio scripsit hanc peticionem.</ab>
                </div>
